H8 : ∀ (x' : X), f x' = x1 → x'' = x',
H9 : x'' = x,
H3 : x1 = f x'
⊢ x = x'
X Y : Type,
f : X → Y,
H1 : bijective f
⊢ surjective f
X Y : Type,
f : X → Y
⊢ injective f ∧ surjective f → bijective f
